{"tid":2489450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭定康與一批議員去信約翰遜：肯制裁香港同新疆班官未 ?","createTime":"2021-04-15T03:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T05:45:00.000Z","uid":21470,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d422f5d48a6f728da110303b19923db4cffda087","tid":2489450,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:09:41.000Z","msg":"彭定康與一批議員去信約翰遜 促制裁損害香港民主官員<br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康與英國過百名跨黨派國會議員，聯署去信首相約翰遜，要求英國政府引用《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁打壓香港民主運動的官員及實體，並且對新疆黨委書記陳全國等侵害新疆維吾爾人權的官員，實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康在信中表示，反對中方上月對多名英國國會議員實施的制裁，認為中方的制裁反映中國政府的威權主義正在擴張，他又認為，英國與中國的所謂「黃金時代」已經過去，敦促英國政府以跨部門方式，盡快檢視策略，以應對中國政府對自由世界帶來的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部在上月底，宣布制裁英方9名人員和4個實體，指他們惡意傳播謊言和虛假信息，中方保留採取進一步措施的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585874-20210415.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585874-20210415.htm&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=00e8e3ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585874-20210415.htm&h=44e7b9c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585874-20210415.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a8d1dd89bd1225cbdc8d914df3c61061d9f30847","tid":2489450,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b916bf06bf8244c6a65d89a7bcfe757b56d6b623","tid":2489450,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8081ec733f2c064bcfbb3b81e52b485ea67410","tid":2489450,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"